{"tid":1918496,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"龍珠招式名應該如何漢化","createTime":"2020-03-10T06:49:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T07:01:31.000Z","uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9995730e0d8495ffbfe7d4656c3f78a67f66053b","tid":1918496,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T06:49:39.000Z","msg":"依家龍珠嘅招式名基本上都唔係好似中文，一般中國嘅武術，都會叫做乜嘢乜嘢掌，或者乜嘢乜嘢功，咁樣嘅。<br />\n不如各位巴打集思廣益，諗下龍珠啲招式名可以點樣譯去打入中國市場。<br />\n例如界王拳，就叫界王混天勁<br />\n龜波氣功，就叫龜仙穿山掌<br />\n太陽拳，日虹貫天<br />\n氣円斬，七旋斬"},{"pid":"1710f8ca6e6aac5ebf05946476b41a1851f21748","tid":1918496,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T06:51:55.000Z","msg":"漢化老母"},{"pid":"5c4ce4c2c5727b97f2ac6ef6dd0deb1cd5d36942","tid":1918496,"uid":11719,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T06:53:39.000Z","msg":"龜波氣功，哈咪哈咪哈"},{"pid":"2577254e550d018cbfa02f6bc2d1aa350d665f8a","tid":1918496,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T06:57:27.000Z","msg":"漢化後，d靚仔叫d名出招。去到秋葉原大叫&rdquo;嘩，呢個界王轟天勁，好型。&rdquo;&rdquo;嘩，好多明星學生妹精品&rdquo; <br />\n好似以前改返中文名幾好，好似<br />\n陳馬<br />\n袁海末<br />\n高千歌"},{"pid":"3baad90c76d71b8ad25155d756abc5a8a33d37a8","tid":1918496,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5c4ce4c2c5727b97f2ac6ef6dd0deb1cd5d36942","tid":1918496,"uid":11719,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T06:53:39.000Z","msg":"龜波氣功，哈咪哈咪哈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T07:01:31.000Z","msg":"直譯應該叫龜龜波"}]}